{
  "texts": [
    "To evaluate the performance of our model for the case studies, we compared it with a baseline GPT-4o-mini model using OpenAI's structured generation.",
    "The prompt used for this model can be found in Appendix E.1.",
    "We evaluated each model using exact match accuracy on frame identification and argument identification (predicting the frame elements of the evoked frame).",
    "These results are presented in Table 1.",
    "Our findings are consistent with a previous study indicating that generative LLMs tend to struggle with frame-semantic parsing (Su et al., 2024)."
  ]
}